.TH "FACADE-AFUNIX" "8" "" "Project Kennel" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
facade\-afunix \- AF_UNIX socket\-shim facade
.SH SYNOPSIS
(internal \(em forked by kenneld(8), not invoked directly)
.SH DESCRIPTION
facade\-afunix is the in\-kennel end of the brokered AF_UNIX socket shim. A granted [[unix.allow]] socket is reached by a binder CONNECT to kenneld, which performs the host\-side connect and returns the connected fd; the real path never enters the kennel view.
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBkenneld\fR(8), \fBkennel\fR(1)
